# Universal Environment Variables
# This is a template for your encrypted .env file
#
# Usage:
#   1. Create .env: ./scripts/env-helper.sh init
#   2. Edit .env:   ./scripts/env-helper.sh edit
#   3. In projects: eval $(~/ansible/scripts/env-helper.sh export)
#
# The .env file will be encrypted with SOPS and safe to commit

